{
  "stem": "1183.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also-- during the war, I had one dream, a recurring dream.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The dream only stopped when I was deported.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a dream there's a big bridge with the Amstel-- River Amstel in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that occurs when I'm in the middle-- lots of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I'm in the middle of the bridge, the bridge opens, and I fall in the water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But before reaching, touching the water, I wake up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was a recurring dream quite often before I was deported.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Afterwards, when I was in the camp, I had no such dream.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this means that the dream is-- was very vivid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still remember that's exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mentioned the first time that my father saved my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was when he pulled me over the drawbridge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The second time was when there was a market, and-- like you have the markets here with groceries, but it was only to be frequented by Jews.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So at that time we had to buy some groceries, and I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said-- my father said, OK, I go with you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went on the market.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We did some shopping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, we heard the motorcycles and the cars coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we knew there was another round-up, because the market was full of Jews, Jewish people who bought their groceries.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was the exact spot for, again, mice or rat in a fault caught in a trap.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My father pulled me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We went just by the exit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when we rounded the corner, the Germans on the motorcycle rounded the corner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So my father turned us around so that they looked at our backs and couldn't see our stars, which we were wearing.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
